<section id="guide-item-bench" class="guide-item">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="gridbox">
            <div>
                <h2>Instalando o controller Bench</h2>
                <p>O controlador Bench te ajuda a comparar metricas de execucao de codigo Ruby.</p>
                <p>Aprenda praticando para destruir nas entrevistas.</p>

                <p><code class="block">lizarb generate bench:install</code></p>
                <p>Veja os exemplos:</p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb bench</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb bench variables</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb bench objects</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb bench loops</code></p>
                <p>Crie os seus:</p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb generate bench hello</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb bench hello</code></p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="/logo.png" alt="logo" style="background-color: black; width: 50%;padding: 100px;">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>



<section id="guide-item-command" class="guide-item">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="gridbox">
            <div>
                <h2>Instalando o controller Command</h2>
                <p>O controlador Command te ajuda a organizar seus scripts Ruby e deixar seu codigo limpo.</p>
                <p>Exercite bons habitos para dominar problemas complexos.</p>

                <p><code class="block">lizarb generate command:install</code></p>
                <p>Veja os exemplos:</p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb command</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb calculator 99 + 1</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb circle area 10</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb quadratic 1 11 30</code></p>
                <p>Crie os seus:</p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb g command hello</code></p>
                <p><code class="block">lizarb hello</code></p>
            </div>
